OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly cloudy with only limited
OL,6,Fbright spells, and scattered showers
OL,7,Fdeveloping. These will be mostly
OL,8,Flight, but there is a chance of
OL,9,Fisolated heavy showers. Temperatures
OL,10,Fslightly lower than previous days, but
OL,11,Fstill warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FScattered showers, a few
OL,14,Fpossibly heavy at first, will fade
OL,15,Faway this evening to leave a dry night
OL,16,Fwith often large amounts of cloud but
OL,17,Falso some clear spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
